## chart main Skillbox Project Status
```mermaid
flowchart TD
  vision["Vision: one private single-tenant Tailnet/Docker dev box for one operator and their coding agents"]
  green["GREEN Proof-backed core: runtime graph render, agent ops brain (capabilities/next/graph/explain/search/snap), client overlays, pulse, installer, skill-distribution sync, worker broker + Codex adapter"]
  yellowEvidence["YELLOW Runtime evidence not green: doctor failing / runtime-sync blocked, covered by skillbox-smart-1-stabilize-runtime-evidence-9t9q + skillbox-gfqm"]
  yellowFriction["YELLOW High-use weak agent surfaces + skill visibility, covered by epics fxm8, 086q, mion"]
  yellowDocs["YELLOW Docs & onboarding + installer workmanship, covered by epic m19o (m19o.6)"]
  redRelease["RED No release/versioning proof: no git tags, no GitHub Releases; no covering Bead"]
  grayInfra["GRAY Side-effecting infra not run this session: up, box-up, provision, teardown, worker launch (disk gate)"]
  next["Next: clear skillbox-gfqm to unblock runtime-sync, then re-run 9t9q to make runtime evidence green"]

  vision --> green
  vision --> yellowEvidence
  vision --> yellowFriction
  vision --> yellowDocs
  vision --> redRelease
  vision --> grayInfra
  yellowEvidence --> next
  redRelease --> next

  class green green
  class yellowEvidence,yellowFriction,yellowDocs yellow
  class redRelease red
  class grayInfra gray
  classDef green fill:#dff7df,stroke:#20833a,stroke-width:2px,color:#0f2f18
  classDef yellow fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#b7791f,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a2a00
  classDef red fill:#ffd6d6,stroke:#c53030,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a0505
  classDef gray fill:#edf2f7,stroke:#718096,stroke-width:2px,color:#1a202c
```

