## chart lifecycle Runtime and Box Lifecycle
```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Declared
  Declared --> Rendered: make render
  Rendered --> Synced: make runtime-sync
  Synced --> Up: make up / runtime-up
  Up --> Healthy: make dev-sanity / doctor
  Healthy --> Down: make down / runtime-down
  Down --> [*]
  Declared --> BoxProvision: make box-up
  BoxProvision --> Enrolled: tailscale enroll
  Enrolled --> PostureLocked: posture-proof (public SSH closed)
  PostureLocked --> Healthy
  Synced --> SyncBlocked: gfqm clone divergence (YELLOW)
  SyncBlocked --> Synced: resolve gfqm
```

## chart architecture-boundary Architecture Boundary
```mermaid
flowchart TB
  subgraph Repo["skillbox repo (single-tenant)"]
    mk["Makefile host/operator commands"]
    rec["scripts/04-reconcile.py outer render/check"]
    rm[".env-manager/runtime_manager CLI + agent ops brain"]
    ws["workspace/*.yaml manifests + client overlays"]
    mcp["scripts/operator_mcp_server.py MCP tools"]
  end
  subgraph State["Durable state (.skillbox-state, logs, invocations)"]
    st["agent homes / clients / snapshots"]
  end
  subgraph Box["Managed box (DigitalOcean + Tailscale)"]
    box["scripts/box.py lifecycle"]
    posture["tailnet_only posture + firewall"]
  end
  subgraph Skills["Skill distribution"]
    repos["skill-repos.yaml (repo/path/distributor)"]
    lock["skill-repos.lock.json (drift, YELLOW)"]
  end

  mk --> rec --> ws
  rm --> ws
  mcp --> rm
  rm --> st
  mk --> box --> posture
  repos --> lock

  class mk,rec,rm,ws,mcp,st,box,posture,repos green
  class lock yellow
  classDef green fill:#dff7df,stroke:#20833a,stroke-width:2px,color:#0f2f18
  classDef yellow fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#b7791f,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a2a00
```

